{
  "stem": "15017.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went right down to Athens, from Athens to Pireaus, from Pireaus to Bari in Italy, by boat, from Italy right up to Milan, and from Milan, by train, through Switzerland, Lausanne, from France to Callais, and then from Callais to Guildford, where there was a whole show of civilian clothes that I wouldn't give to a dog.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because who had civilian clothes during the war, nice civilian clothes?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, I got demobilized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came home, out of the Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'd always kept in touch with the guys in the business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no sooner did I get home, got my daughter, went to Mom and Dad, went to Mom and Dad with my daughter, I phoned the boys that I was home.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, thank God you're home!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Come in to work tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you see, I was very, very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Amongst the number-one musicians in London, they gave an audition to the guard's bands, which meant they had to sign up for 12 years or any part thereof before they were accepted.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were stationed in Buckingham Palace, which was Birdcage Walk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were stationed at the Tower of London.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were stationed at Windsor, so they could come in and do their jobs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after the war finished, these guys couldn't do anything, because they had to do victory parades.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's where I came in, started to earn money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, those guys bought themselves out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So whatever they earned, they paid for it to get out the Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But anyhow, I came home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I started work and saw that my daughter went to a boarding school in Byfleet, which is in Surrey.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was costing 15 pounds a semester, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everything went on fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
